              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                Denton County is home to the University of North Texas, Texas Woman's 
                University, and a diverse range of businesses from education to 
                manufacturing. Our team provides reliable cleaning services that help 
                Denton County businesses maintain clean, professional environments.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                From the college town atmosphere of Denton to the growing suburbs of 
                Lewisville and Flower Mound, we understand the unique needs of Denton 
                County businesses and deliver customized cleaning solutions.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-lg p-6">
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Why Choose Dream Cleaned for Denton County?</h3>
                <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <CheckCircle className="h-4 w-4 text-brand-gold mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <span>Local team familiar with Denton County regulations</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <CheckCircle className="h-4 w-4 text-brand-gold mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <span>Flexible scheduling for busy Denton businesses</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <CheckCircle className="h-4 w-4 text-brand-gold mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <span>Emergency cleaning services available</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <CheckCircle className="h-4 w-4 text-brand-gold mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" />
                    <span>Competitive pricing for Denton County market</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-card p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Denton County Quick Facts</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <MapPin className="h-5 w-5 text-brand-gold mr-3" />
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">County Seat</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Denton</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <Users className="h-5 w-5 text-brand-gold mr-3" />
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Population</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">900K+</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <CheckCircle className="h-5 w-5 text-brand-gold mr-3" />
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Major Industries</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Education, Manufacturing, Healthcare, Retail</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center">
                  <Clock className="h-5 w-5 text-brand-gold mr-3" />
                  <div>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Service Response</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">Next Day</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Cities and Towns Section -->
